dcterms:description: A dataset comprising fetal ultrasound videos collected as part of the PULSE project, used for detecting out-of-distribution samples in fetal ultrasound videos.
dcterms:title: Fetal Ultrasound Dataset

dcterms:description: An in-distribution dataset consisting of 5 standard heart views captured during obstetric ultrasound scanning.
dcterms:title: In-distribution dataset (5 standard heart views)

dcterms:description: An out-of-distribution dataset comprising three non-heart anatomies: fetal head, abdomen, and femur.
dcterms:title: Out-of-distribution dataset (three non-heart anatomies)

dcterms:description: A held-out dataset consisting of 7471 images, including different heart views and out-of-distribution classes.
dcterms:title: Held-out dataset (7471 images)
